-- Merko Ehitus Fourth-Quarter Loss Widens on Asset Writedown
-- B y   O t t   U m m e l a s
-- 2012-02-22T14:45:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-22/merko-ehitus-fourth-quarter-loss-widens-on-asset-writedown.html
Merko Ehitus AS, the biggest listed
Baltic builder, said its loss in the fourth quarter widened to 6
million euros ($7.9 million) from 4 million euros a year
earlier, citing a writedown of its property assets in the three
Baltic countries by 6 million euros, according to a regulatory
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
